All Implemented Interfaces:
ArchetypeVertex, Cloneable, Element, Hypervertex, UserDataContainer
public class ListHypervertex
extends CollectionHypervertex

An implementation of Hypervertex that stores its incident edges as a List internally. This is space-efficient, but most methods require time proportional to the degree of the vertex, and some (findEdge) may take more.

Author:
Joshua O'Madadhain
